PN,31201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772809880
OL,3,CAsylum seekers who break law or work
OL,4,Cillegally to lose right to
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FAsylum seekers who break the law, work
OL,8,Fillegally, or are able to financially
OL,9,Fsupport themselves will lose the right
OL,10,Fto government-funded accommodation
OL,11,Funder new plans to be announced on
OL,12,FThursday.
OL,14,FThe rule change means only those with
OL,15,Flegitimate asylum claims who follow
OL,16,Fthe rules will get taxpayer-funded
OL,17,Fsupport, Home Secretary Shabana
OL,18,FMahmood said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772809880
OL,3,CAsylum seekers who break law or work
OL,4,Cillegally to lose right to
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FThe new measures are being announced
OL,8,Fas part of a major shake-up of the
OL,9,FUK's immigration system, adding to the
OL,10,Fgovernment's raft of reforms announced
OL,11,Fin November.
OL,13,FThe statutory legal duty under EU law
OL,14,Fto provide asylum seekers with support
OL,15,Fand accommodation will be replaced
OL,16,Fwith a conditional approach.
OL,18,FThe government is determined to make
OL,19,Fthe UK a less attractive destination
OL,20,Ffor illegal migrants.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772809880
OL,3,CAsylum seekers who break law or work
OL,4,Cillegally to lose right to
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FThe home secretary is also expected to
OL,8,Fannounce that the English language
OL,9,Ftest for people seeking permanent
OL,10,Fsettlement will be made tougher, and
OL,11,Fthat foreign nationals with suspended
OL,12,Fsentences of a year or more will be
OL,13,Frefused entry to the country.
OL,15,FHer speech comes less than a week
OL,16,Fafter Labour's bruising by-election
OL,17,Floss in Gorton and Denton, where the
OL,18,FGreens won a historic victory with a
OL,19,Fmajority of more than 4,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772809880
OL,3,CAsylum seekers who break law or work
OL,4,Cillegally to lose right to
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FThe Green win has sparked calls from
OL,8,Fsome on the left of the Labour Party
OL,9,Ffor the government to be less hardline
OL,10,Fon immigration, but Mahmood has made
OL,11,Fit clear she intends to double down,
OL,12,Fwhile insisting her reforms are led by
OL,13,F"Labour values".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772809880
OL,3,CAsylum seekers who break law or work
OL,4,Cillegally to lose right to
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FShe said on Thursday that her changes
OL,8,Fto the system are "firm but fair",
OL,9,Foutlining the case for a position
OL,10,Fbetween Reform leader Nigel Farage's
OL,11,F"nightmare pulling up the drawbridge
OL,12,Fand shutting out the world" and Green
OL,13,FParty leader Zack Polanski's "fairy
OL,14,Ftale of open borders".
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@[O]uD@^OUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772809880
OL,3,CAsylum seekers who break law or work
OL,4,Cillegally to lose right to
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,FMahmood, who is facing a potential
OL,8,Frebellion from Labour backbenchers
OL,9,Fover the plans, said in her speech at
OL,10,Fthe centre-left think tank IPPR in
OL,11,FLondon: "If we cannot deal with so
OL,12,Fvisible a failure, what can the state
OL,13,Fachieve at all?
OL,15,F"It is our creed, as the Labour Party,
OL,16,Fthat the state can and must be a force
OL,17,Ffor good.
OL,26,@sD@IOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772809880
OL,3,CAsylum seekers who break law or work
OL,4,Cillegally to lose right to
OL,5,Caccommodation
OL,7,F"Without the trust of citizens in the
OL,8,Fstate, therefore, there is no space
OL,9,Ffor Labour values ` in any part of
OL,10,Fgovernment ` to be realised.
OL,12,F"Restoring order and control at our
OL,13,Fborder is not a betrayal of Labour
OL,14,Fvalues, it is an embodiment of them,
OL,15,Fand it is the necessary condition for
OL,16,Fa Labour government to achieve
OL,17,Fanything it hopes to."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
